{"tid":2264139,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中年漢向露宿者兜頭屙尿跪地求和 露宿者陳伯大方回應：「唔緊要」　","createTime":"2020-10-30T11:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T12:57:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d48a1d6d8c511089eb5314cc2273c7824f9e94b6","tid":2264139,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》今晨到場找到該名露宿者，他仍挨在走火通道的門口角落，一副懶洋洋的樣子。他姓陳，自言僅在此露宿十多天，談到昨天有否被淋尿，他說：「佢屙喺地下啫，彈唔到我，唔緊要，以前冇試過！」他說以前住宿舍，現在租不到地方住，所以露宿街頭。他坦言有攞綜援，「冇嘢做，租唔到地方。」他說昨天向他屙尿的男子，他不認識亦不曾見過，對於會否嬲他，陳伯點起香煙，頻頻說：「唔緊要」，被問到該中年漢知否他在該處仍照屙尿？陳伯說：「就算知都唔緊要」。他又感謝昨夜出手幫他的市民。他其後持着雨傘，緩緩而行，離開門口角落，但角落仍留有他的衣褲、四支樽裝水等物品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201030/C534AK6ROZAINJWSNT53Q5WPMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201030%2FC534AK6ROZAINJWSNT53Q5WPMQ%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdtTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=4fd4b6b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201030%2FC534AK6ROZAINJWSNT53Q5WPMQ%2F&h=e51a5299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201030/C534AK6ROZAINJWSNT53Q5WPMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"5ae4e5ab05eb8fec62b8125d818dd7f9c6ca4937","tid":2264139,"uid":21267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"鬥黃（啲尿)"},{"pid":"2aa7a0d70d9b9ebc84fd356cf020b7a88f9ff3b6","tid":2264139,"uid":293296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03da938e03c90d321aa1ed1c808fbcf9ab47db06","tid":2264139,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf2edaf7768aa9940d84f067a94483a3774162f","tid":2264139,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"佢應該喺嗰度露宿左唔止10幾日<br />\n成個月都有"}]}